txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Mucky filth from swamp-dwelling creatures in the Dunbog. Collect them and deliver them to the taskmaster in Galtrev to earn favour with the Men of Dunland.
'I hate those creepy things. Good riddance to them all!'
'There are...things in the Dunbog that come creeping out at night, and for years we have kept them at bay within the swamp. Help us, if you will.'
Men of Dunland Task: Mucky Filth
The Dunlending taskmaster wants mucky filth. She can be found at Galtrev in Pren Gwydh.
Deliver the mucky filth to the taskmaster in Galtrev.
You have accepted a task to acquire mucky filth. You are to deliver it to the Dunlending taskmaster in Galtrev.
Wanted: Mucky filth from swamp-dwelling creatures in the Dunbog.
